<%- include('./partials/header') %>

    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid bg-dark text-white rounded">
            <div class="container p-3">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h1 class="m-3">
                        Welcome to Splitter!
                    </h1>
                    <div class="px-5 pb-3">
                        <p>Splitter makes it simple to divide bills and daily expenses among friends, family, and foes.
                            Here are a few things you need to know to get started.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="pb-3">
                        <ul class="list-unstyled px-3">
                            <li class="p-1">&#127919; Start off by creating a session. A session is <kbd
                                    class="bg-light text-dark">1 hour</kbd> long. All data will be <kbd
                                    class="bg-light text-dark">automatically deleted</kbd> once the session ends.</li>
                            <li class="p-1">&#127919; Once you start a session, you cannot create another session in
                                parallel. You can end the session anytime by coming to this home page or
                                right after completing the bill.</li>
                            <li class="p-1">&#127919; You need to add atleast <kbd class="bg-light text-dark">2
                                    members</kbd> to start adding expenses. Member names must be unique.</li>
                            <li class="p-1">&#127919; You may or may not wish to enter item name while adding expenses;
                                it's <kbd class="bg-light text-dark">optional.</kbd></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <p>That's all...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="my-5 text-center">
            <a href="/create" class="btn btn-dark m-1 <%= sessionExists==true?'disabled':null %>">Create Session</a>
            <% if(sessionExists) { %>
                <a href="/end" class="btn btn-dark m-1">End Session</a>
                <a href="/addmember" class="btn btn-dark m-1">Next</a>
                <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>